%AI_Design_Template_for_Box_Pouch
%Package_Lab_Epackage_Design_Template
%Japanese_Market_Standard_Dimensions

Template_Name: BOX型パウチ (Box Pouch)
Product_Category: box
Standard_Sizes:
  - 120mm x 80mm x 40mm
  - 150mm x 100mm x 50mm
  - 180mm x 120mm x 60mm
  - 200mm x 140mm x 70mm

Design_Specifications:
  - Bleed: 3mm on all edges
  - Safety Zone: 5mm from edges
  - File Format: Adobe Illustrator CS6 or later
  - Color Mode: CMYK
  - Resolution: 300 DPI
  - Includes all 6 panels (Front, Back, Top, Bottom, Left, Right)

Cutting_Guides:
  - Solid line: Final cut line
  - Dashed line: Fold lines
  - Cross marks: Registration points

Design_Elements:
  [Front_Panel]
  - Product logo area: Top center
  - Product name: Below logo
  - Product description: Center area
  - Weight/Volume: Bottom left
  - Barcode area: Bottom right

  [Back_Panel]
  - Ingredients list: Top area
  - Instructions: Center area
  - Manufacturer info: Bottom area
  - Expiry date: Bottom right
  - Recycling symbols: Bottom corner

  [Top_Panel]
  - QR code: Center
  - Opening instructions: Below QR code
  - Brand tagline: Top area

  [Bottom_Panel]
  - Nutrition information (if applicable)
  - Storage instructions
  - Best before date

  [Side_Panels_Left/Right]
  - Nutritional highlights
  - Marketing claims
  - Certifications (organic, halal, etc.)

Color_Guidelines:
  - Primary colors: Brand specific
  - Text color: High contrast (minimum 60%)
  - Background: Consider premium positioning
  - Each panel can have unique color scheme

Special_Features:
  - Premium appearance
  - High protection for contents
  - Shelf stability
  - Easy to stack
  - Re-sealable options available

File_Naming_Convention:
  - Client_Project_ProductCode_Size.ai
  - Example: Epackage_Premium_Brand_BoxPouch_150x100x50.ai

